Program: Outlook
Title: Life after the Mudslides in Guatemala
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbs57
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Life for one Guatemalan family after 2005 landslide. Also the plight of elderly Indian widows temple chanting for money because of a lack of family support. Top scientists at SETI searching for aliens. Presenter: Frederick Dove.